headline: IQVIA Named to the Fortune® World’s Most Admired Companies™ List, Ranked No. 1 in Its Sector for Fifth Consecutive Year
summary: RESEARCH TRIANGLE PARK, N.C., January 22, 2026--IQVIA (NYSE:IQV), a leading global provider of clinical research services, commercial insights and healthcare intelligence, was named No. 1 in its category on the 2026 Fortune® World’s Most Admired Companies™ list.
